sbl-desc: A [https://semantic-mediawiki.org Semantic MediaWiki] extension to build breadcrumb links from an attributive property filter
smw-pa-property-predefined__sbl_parentpa: "$1" is a predefined property that can describe a relationship between a parent and a child entity and is provided by the [https://www.semantic-mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Semantic_Breadcrumb_Links Semantic Breadcrumb Links] extension.
smw-pa-property-predefined-long__sbl_par: By identifying the location of an entity relative to its parent it can be used to generate a navigational help in form of a breadcrumb trail.
